    </coordinates>
    <panel_attributes>&lt;&lt;arc42 Whitebox&gt;&gt;
StudyPilot Backend (Node.js + Express)
--
Responsibilities:
- Authentication and authorization
- Course/task/document/user APIs
- Storage + realtime + persistence</panel_attributes>
    <additional_attributes/>
  </element>
  <element>
    <id>UMLClass</id>
    <coordinates>
      <x>108</x>
      <y>189</y>
      <w>270</w>
      <h>153</h>
    </coordinates>
    <panel_attributes>1. Entry + Infrastructure
--
index.ts
- Express app + HTTP server
- Socket.IO server
- Passport init
- Swagger docs
- global error handler</panel_attributes>
    <additional_attributes/>
  </element>
  <element>
    <id>UMLClass</id>
    <coordinates>
      <x>414</x>
      <y>189</y>
      <w>270</w>
      <h>171</h>
    </coordinates>
    <panel_attributes>2. Routing Layer
--
routes/index.ts + modules
- auth.routes
- course.routes
- task.routes
- user.routes
- document.routes
- storage.routes
- health endpoint</panel_attributes>
    <additional_attributes/>
  </element>
  <element>
    <id>UMLClass</id>
    <coordinates>
      <x>720</x>
      <y>189</y>
      <w>297</w>
      <h>171</h>
    </coordinates>
    <panel_attributes>3. Controller Layer
--
controllers/*
- validates request data
- maps HTTP to use-cases
- maps errors to status codes</panel_attributes>
    <additional_attributes/>
  </element>
  <element>
    <id>UMLClass</id>
    <coordinates>
